---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="container-wide pb-8 pt-6">
  <div class="panel overflow-hidden rounded-[20px] px-7 py-8 md:px-10 md:py-9">
    <div class="glow-divider mb-6"></div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <p class="eyebrow">Slow Notes, Bright Ideas</p>
        <h2 class="section-title mt-3 text-xl md:text-2xl">慢慢写，持续更新</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[0.9rem] leading-relaxed text-[var(--muted)]">
          这里收集教程、学习记录和一些正在发酵的灵感，让每次更新都更耐读一点
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-[0.85rem] text-[var(--muted)] md:text-right">
        <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text-strong)]">&copy; {year} 梦付千秋</p>
        <p class="mt-1.5">
          Built with
          <a
            href="https://astro.build"
            class="text-[var(--accent-strong)] underline decoration-[rgba(124,179,240,0.35)] underline-offset-4"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >
            Astro
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
